{
  "page": "Greywater fever",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Greywater fever</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Disease\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Disease\">disease</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> It is possible it is endemic to <a href=\"/index.php/The_Neck\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The Neck\">the Neck</a>, as it shares the name of <a href=\"/index.php/Greywater_Watch\" title=\"Greywater Watch\">Greywater Watch</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_events\">Recent events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Greywater_fever&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Greywater_fever&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Jojen_Reed\" title=\"Jojen Reed\">Jojen Reed</a> tells <a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran Stark</a> he nearly died of greywater fever during his childhood. While he was near death, he was visited in dreams by a <a href=\"/index.php/Three-eyed_crow\" title=\"Three-eyed crow\">three-eyed crow</a> that gave him the gift of <a href=\"/index.php/Greensight\" title=\"Greensight\">greendreams</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Greywater_fever&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_28\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 28\">Chapter 28</a>, Bran IV.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403145839\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.016 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.017 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 188/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8576/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 704/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 44/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 804/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   11.216      1 -total\n 77.20%    8.658      2 Template:Ref\n 52.73%    5.914      2 Template:Ref/core\n 20.70%    2.322      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:23121-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403145839 and revision id 289577